{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"1030a","heading":"Eliminating unnecessary plan requirements related to unenrolled participants","label":"1030a Eliminating unnecessary plan requirements related to unenrolled participants","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/ch18/schI/stB/pt1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe Internal Revenue Code of 1986, referred to in subsec. (b)(2)(B), is classified generally to Title 26, Internal Revenue Code.","Prior ProvisionsA prior was renumbered section 112 and is classified to .section 111 of Pub. L. 93–406section 1031 of this title","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective DateSection applicable to plan years beginning after , see , set out as an Effective Date of 2022 Amendment note under , Internal Revenue Code.Dec. 31, 2022section 320(c) of Pub. L. 117–328section 414 of Title 26"],"amendments":["Effective DateSection applicable to plan years beginning after , see , set out as an Effective Date of 2022 Amendment note under , Internal Revenue Code.Dec. 31, 2022section 320(c) of Pub. L. 117–328section 414 of Title 26"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an annual reminder notice of such participant’s eligibility to participate in such plan and any applicable election deadlines under the plan; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any document requested by such participant that the participant would be entitled to receive notwithstanding this section.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Unenrolled participant","label":"b Unenrolled participant","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is eligible to participate in an individual account plan;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fb%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the summary plan description pursuant to , andsection 1024(b) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fb%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any other notices related to eligibility under the plan required to be furnished under this subchapter, or the Internal Revenue Code of 1986, in connection with such participant’s initial eligibility to participate in such plan;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is not participating in such plan; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"satisfies such other criteria as the Secretary of Labor may determine appropriate, as prescribed in guidance issued in consultation with the Secretary of Treasury.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Annual reminder notice","label":"c Annual reminder notice","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is furnished in connection with the annual open season election period with respect to the plan or, if there is no such period, is furnished within a reasonable period prior to the beginning of each plan year;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fc%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the unenrolled participant’s eligibility to participate in the plan; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fc%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the key benefits and rights under the plan, with a focus on employer contributions and vesting provisions; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1030a/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft29%2Fs1030a%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"provides such information in a prominent manner calculated to be understood by the average participant.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
